    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2020 sedan in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable scratches and some dents, with visible wear in multiple areas. The car runs and drives but has some components that will need attention in the near to medium term. The interior has moderate wear including some staining and worn surfaces. Overall a functional vehicle with clear cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
